## Key Results

| Model               | Accuracy | F1    | AUC-ROC |
|---------------------|----------|-------|---------|
| Random Forest       | ~87%     | ~86%  | ~0.92   |
| SVM                 | ~83%     | ~82%  | ~0.89   |
| Logistic Regression | ~80%     | ~77%  | ~0.85   |

- Features reduced from 20 → 14 (30% reduction via SelectFromModel)
- Preprocessing automated via `sklearn.Pipeline` — one `.fit()` call
- `predictions_powerbi.csv` contains CustomerID, Churn_Probability, Risk_Tier

