## Power BI Dashboard

Connect `predictions_powerbi.csv` to Power BI Desktop.

**Recommended slicers:** Contract · InternetService · Risk_Tier  
**Recommended visuals:** KPI cards · Donut chart · Scatter · Bar chart · Table  

**DAX measures:**
```dax
Churn Rate = 
  DIVIDE(
    COUNTROWS(FILTER(predictions_powerbi, [Churn_Actual] = 1)),
    COUNTROWS(predictions_powerbi)
  )

Model Accuracy = 
  DIVIDE(
    COUNTROWS(FILTER(predictions_powerbi, [Churn_Actual] = [Churn_Predicted])),
    COUNTROWS(predictions_powerbi)
  )
```

