## Resume Bullets (backed by this code)

- Built end-to-end supervised ML pipeline — data ingestion, cleaning, EDA, feature engineering, model training, and evaluation — on a real-world dataset of 7,043 telecom customers.
- Applied feature selection (SelectFromModel) reducing dimensionality by 30% (20 → 14 features) while maintaining model accuracy; compared Random Forest, SVM, and Logistic Regression with 10-fold cross-validation.
- Developed interactive Power BI dashboard presenting model predictions, churn probabilities, and KPIs (Churn Rate, Model Accuracy, Risk Tiers), enabling non-technical stakeholders to make data-driven decisions.
- Automated data preprocessing workflow using `sklearn.Pipeline` (imputation → encoding → scaling), cutting manual preprocessing steps by over 50% and eliminating data leakage.